867
00:48:40,760 --> 00:48:42,960
Senhoras e senhores, Paris Hilton,

868
00:48:43,040 --> 00:48:46,440
e o entusiasta de golfe
mais rápido do mundo, Rory McIlroy.

869
00:48:51,440 --> 00:48:52,680
Agora!

870
00:48:53,080 --> 00:48:57,200
Mais cedo, estávamos no Canadá,

871
00:48:57,280 --> 00:49:01,760
